Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.41,0:01:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you get serious for a moment,\NInspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long do you intend\Nto detain all of my guests?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.79,0:01:56.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have any more time to be part of your fruitless investigation!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.13,0:01:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, now, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.33,0:02:01.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The victim {\i1}was{\i0} a guest invited to your partyâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,President Yamazaki of Yatsubishi Bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.13,0:02:07.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please have a little more patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.44,0:02:10.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting that the one responsible is in this room?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.04,0:02:11.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:15.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The door was locked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.34,0:02:18.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer entered from the next window over on the third floor
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:20.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and then left the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.68,0:02:22.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There were no footprints below the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:26.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which points to the fact that this was an inside job.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:29.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nonsense! It's almost 10 meters\Nto the next window!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.86,0:02:31.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jumping from one to the other is impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.93,0:02:35.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the killer used the edge of the roof to get across to the next window,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:37.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there would be less than\N2 meters left to the veranda
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.60,0:02:40.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,of the room where Mr. Yamazaki was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.44,0:02:41.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What childish reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.74,0:02:44.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So how did the killer leave then?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.17,0:02:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way they could have jumped the 2 meters to the roof edge,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.48,0:02:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,which only sticks 10 centimeters out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.45,0:02:55.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The killer brought some rope when leaving the next room over,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:59.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,affixed it to the veranda,\Nand then later used it to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:03.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then how was the rope removed from the veranda afterward?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.99,0:03:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's simple, Inspector Megure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stick was tied to one end of the rope\Nand attached to the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.23,0:03:11.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It easily came undone when tugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.10,0:03:15.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Check the veranda.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should find marks from when the rope was affixed to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:22.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what was Mr. Yamazaki doing inside a locked room?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:26.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Most likely, the killer told him\Nto wait there with the door locked
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.28,0:03:30.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,because he had something important and secret to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.69,0:03:32.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've had enough of your pompous talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.35,0:03:36.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just who was it who broke in and killed Mr. Yamazaki, my best friend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.03,0:03:38.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is only one person who knows enough of this house's layout
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.03,0:03:43.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and who could walk throughout it\Nwithout raising any suspicion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.40,0:03:45.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.38,0:03:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None other than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must be joking!\NMy leg hasn't even healed yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.55,0:04:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.92,0:04:09.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Your leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:11.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.23,0:04:14.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your leg healed 3 months ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.66,0:04:16.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Inspector Megure?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.47,0:04:17.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:20.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your physician has disclosed everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.54,0:04:22.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We also know that you and your best friend Mr. Yamazaki
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:26.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,had under-the-table financial dealings.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.81,0:04:28.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh no you don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:31.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Goal!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.48,0:04:40.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm really in your debt, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.19,0:04:42.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks for always being there to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you run into any other difficult cases,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.30,0:04:49.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,feel free to contact me, Detective Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.75,0:05:08.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.62,0:05:13.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me a break here, Dr. Agasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just thought I'd wake you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:19.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Works better than an alarm clock,\Nwouldn't you agree?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.86,0:05:24.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number of books you have here\Nnever ceases to amaze me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}was{\i0} because of all these
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.10,0:05:30.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that your father was able to become an international mystery writer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.84,0:05:32.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop moving around, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.69,0:05:34.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What were you testing this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.04,0:05:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell this to anyone, got it?!\NThis is just between you and me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.08,0:05:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a Personal Mobility Rocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.65,0:05:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Once I perfect it, traffic jams will become a thing of the past
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.35,0:05:49.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and I'll be filthy rich!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.96,0:05:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are these? Oh, books.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:08.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dammit! That stupid kid again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.51,0:06:10.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get a hold of yourself, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.81,0:06:13.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's 'cuz he's a high school student playing a detective
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,that I hardly ever get any jobs anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:18.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.\NShin'ichi is just really good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.82,0:06:20.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to make a living, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:23.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to school now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:25.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Go wherever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:27.96,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The famous detective Shin'ichi Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:29.83,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The modern-day Japanese Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.83,0:06:33.27,Radio,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Also considered by many as the savior\Nof the Japanese police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.64,0:06:36.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi Kudo is so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.74,0:06:39.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe I should write him a love letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.61,0:06:47.32,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ran Mouri\N2nd year student, Teitan High
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.85,0:06:47.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're so stupid!\NGrinning like you're some big shot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.78,0:06:49.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you so angry about, Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not mad at all that my dad\Ncan't get any work because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.83,0:07:03.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not my fault your dad doesn't\Nget much work, he's just not good at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.93,0:07:10.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I told you, I'm not mad at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.14,0:07:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just what I'd expect from the head of the karate club...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:32.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't quit the soccer club,\Nyou would've been a big hero here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.83,0:07:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only did soccer to acquire the physical prowess that all detectives need!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.67,0:07:41.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Holmes had his fencing, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.74,0:07:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But those are just novels.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.84,0:07:46.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's a detective that everyone's heard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.04,0:07:48.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's so amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's always calm and composed\Nno matter the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.01,0:07:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,and he's practically overflowing\Nwith intelligence and refinement!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:57.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And his keen powers of observation\Nand deduction are unparalleled!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:08:00.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On top of that, his violin skills\Nare equal to those of a professional!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.82,0:08:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan Doyle's Sherlock Holmes\Nis the world's greatest detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.93,0:08:13.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you like him so much, why don't you become a writer like your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.54,0:08:17.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't want to write about detectives, I want to {\i1}be{\i0} one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.51,0:08:20.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The modern-day Japanese Sherlock Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.44,0:08:25.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The exhilaration from catching\Nthe bad guys is beyond description!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.95,0:08:28.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Try being a detective once\Nand there's no going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.28,0:08:32.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And look at all these fan letters!\NDetectives are popular!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.72,0:08:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's fine that you're always flirting with girls,\Nbut at least choose a favorite!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.73,0:08:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:47.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What're you staring at?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:51.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, nothing! We better hurry or we'll miss class!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.78,0:08:56.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You haven't forgotten your promise for tomorrow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:58.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:08:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.61,0:09:05.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said if I won the karate tournament\Nthat you'd take me to Tropical Land!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sicko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.06,0:09:11.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I... remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:43.20,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ayumi Yoshida
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:46.63,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Genta Kojima
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.20,0:09:46.63,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhiko Tsuburaya
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.49,0:09:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was so totally fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.39,0:09:45.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it was so totally bad for the heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:46.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.62,0:09:50.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,For a big guy you sure\Nget scared easy, Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.43,0:09:53.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the Mystery Coaster should be okay for you two, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:57.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, we only have enough left for the train back home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.01,0:10:01.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's fine! Just leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.35,0:10:12.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, look, Shin'ichi! There's room on the Mystery Coaster! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:18.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tryin' to sneak in for free, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.56,0:10:21.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, kids these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.90,0:10:30.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The coolest thing about Holmes is when he first met his assistant Watson,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.14,0:10:35.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,he could tell he went to Afghanistan as a military doctor just by shaking his hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.38,0:10:37.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.61,0:10:42.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're in a gymnastics club, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:43.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-How did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.62,0:10:45.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you know him, Hitomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.66,0:10:49.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was the blisters on her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:54.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only girls who train on the horizontal bar\Never get this many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.86,0:10:58.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you can get blisters doing tennis too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.17,0:11:03.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I saw earlier when\Nthe wind blew her skirt up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.84,0:11:05.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only those with experience on the horizontal bar
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,get marks like that on their thighs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.91,0:11:11.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not fair if you knew from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.51,0:11:15.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to keep holding her hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.58,0:11:16.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.65,0:11:19.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Quit botherin' my pals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.92,0:11:23.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A friend of yours? In that case, why don't we switch places in line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:25.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Plus it'd be impolite to disturb Aiko and Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.80,0:11:36.87,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.87,0:11:38.81,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I've liked you ever since I wasâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.81,0:11:40.07,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.07,0:11:41.28,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:42.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:43.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go! We can get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.75,0:11:45.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.81,0:11:47.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now what do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:50.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we just get in line for seats!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.32,0:11:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which way is the line?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what we're trying to find out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.82,0:11:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...and then Holmes...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:12:00.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Out of the way! We're first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:07.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So do you see? Conan Doyle must have wanted to be like Holmes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.94,0:12:13.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cut it out with Holmes and Doyle,\Nyou big mystery geek!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:20.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I looked so forward to coming here with you, Shin'ichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.95,0:12:24.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why can't you see the way I feel about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.09,0:12:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.49,0:12:29.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, actually, I feel the sameâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.62,0:12:31.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Got you! What're you so nervous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.86,0:12:33.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm obviously just kidding around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.86,0:12:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't make a good detective if you're tricked so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.34,0:12:43.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.61,0:12:46.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did look forward to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:12.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.97,0:13:14.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's get the heck outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:20.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.79,0:13:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those are police cars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.62,0:13:36.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:38.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We didn't sneak in for free!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.23,0:13:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you that high school detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:46.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi Kudo's the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.34,0:13:54.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How horrible...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.28,0:13:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to loiter around because of an ordinary accident!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.48,0:13:59.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let us leave already.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.61,0:14:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wrong! This was a murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.28,0:14:07.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the culprit was one of the seven other people on the roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:10.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi! Where did you go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that the truth, Kudo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! Kudo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.96,0:14:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Shin'ichi Kudo, the famous high school student detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.17,0:14:21.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's the savior of the Japanese police department!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:24.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he's Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.67,0:14:28.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, temporarily taking you and Ran{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} out of the picture,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.88,0:14:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,there were 5 passengers total.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:35.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Passengers A and B in the first row were both friends of the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:41.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,C, who was both friend and girlfriend to the victim, was in the third row.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.39,0:14:46.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And D and E were the men in black who sat behind the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:50.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But everyone had their safety guards on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.13,0:14:55.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,so only the woman sitting next to him could have committed the murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.50,0:14:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.31,0:15:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have time for your little detective games!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:04.64,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}What with this guy's icy stare?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.08,0:15:08.08,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's glaring like he's killed lots of people before without a second thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.08,0:15:10.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}W-Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.02,0:15:13.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector! There's a knife in this woman's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.65,0:15:16.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way! I've never seen that before in my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.86,0:15:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aiko! And I thought you and Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} were on good terms...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:22.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:24.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No! I didn't do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.43,0:15:26.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's obvious the girl did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.50,0:15:28.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be leaving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.50,0:15:31.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright! Take her into custody as the prime suspect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.84,0:15:33.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She isn't the murderer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:38.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh?! T-Then who is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.85,0:15:44.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There is always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.79,0:15:49.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one responsible...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.12,0:15:50.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,...is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:07.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,W-What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The knife was in Aiko's purse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:12.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Severing a person's head with such a knife would be impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.35,0:16:15.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Especially for a young woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You put the knife in Aiko's purse\Nin advance to put the blame on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But she was sitting in the very front row!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.63,0:16:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that make it impossible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.23,0:16:29.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's entirely possible if she utilized the coaster's speed
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.46,0:16:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,in conjunction with a bit\Nof piano wire or some rope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.67,0:16:36.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Everyone ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:39.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm the murderer, and Inspector Megure is the victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,First, before pulling the safety guard down,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:45.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I put a purse-like object behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the guard comes down and... See?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.08,0:16:50.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the extra space, it's easy to slip out.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.32,0:16:57.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, I take out a pre-prepared rope with a hook at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.66,0:17:01.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I put my legs around the guard, stretch back, and place the rope loop
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.59,0:17:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,around the victim's neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:06.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All while inside a pitch-black tunnel, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.93,0:17:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I attach the hook to the rail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:14.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After this, the coaster's speed and power will take the head right off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.67,0:17:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As a gymnast, doing all of this while on the coaster is entirely plausible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.61,0:17:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is crazy! What proof do you have...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:25.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to your necklace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.22,0:17:28.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The pearl necklace you were wearing before you got on the ride.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.62,0:17:32.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this not it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.73,0:17:41.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your tears served as another clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.67,0:17:44.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew beforehand that the victim was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.80,0:17:46.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which is why you silently wept before doing him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.34,0:17:52.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The trails of tears that go horizontally across your face...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The only way your tears could have flowed horizontally
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.95,0:17:57.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,was if you were crying while on the coaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.62,0:18:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was his fault, I tell you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.63,0:18:07.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He forsook me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.79,0:18:11.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hitomi, you were going out with Kishida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.10,0:18:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right! Long before I met you two in college!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.00,0:18:20.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why I decided to kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.81,0:18:28.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,where we had our very first date,\Nusing the necklace he gave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.75,0:19:07.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.09,0:19:09.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't affected one bit, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.46,0:19:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm used to crime scenes now.\NYou know, torn up bodies and stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.43,0:19:15.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's horrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.16,0:19:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's best to forget about it as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These sorta things happen all the time, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.53,0:19:20.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They do not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.11,0:19:30.04,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Huh? It's one of the men in black\Nfrom the roller coaster...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:33.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ran! You go on ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:35.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waitâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.45,0:19:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll catch up with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:41.75,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}He's leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.20,0:19:55.69,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm not sure why, but I could just tell somehow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:20:02.67,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I got the horrible feeling\Nthat I'd never see Shin'ichi again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:15.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, Company Director.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.62,0:20:19.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're late! I've been waiting for two hours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.29,0:20:20.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came alone, just as I promised!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I know. I rode the roller coaster\Nand checked from above.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.67,0:20:27.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just hurry and give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get ahead of yourself!\NThe money comes first!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.64,0:20:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here! I take it you have no objections?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.77,0:20:35.11,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Whoa! There's at least 100 million in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.11,0:20:36.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This concludes our transaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.98,0:20:38.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry and give me the film!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.44,0:20:41.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The incriminating film that shows your company smuggling weapons?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.85,0:20:43.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.85,0:20:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is all of the film, right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:48.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.06,0:20:52.52,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Who in the world are these people?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.96,0:20:56.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's enough of your little detective game.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.67,0:21:02.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was just our luck, having this\Npunk kid follow us around...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.87,0:21:04.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't he that detective, boss?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.80,0:21:05.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Want me to take care of him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:08.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No. The place is still crawlin' with cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.41,0:21:13.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll use this. Our organization's latest poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.18,0:21:18.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't even show up in autopsies.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been tested on humans yet,\Nbut let's consider this a trial run.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.62,0:21:27.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So long, Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.87,0:21:42.27,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}M-My body's burning up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:49.35,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's like my bones are melting!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.35,0:21:51.98,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I can't hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.04,0:23:26.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! There's a dead body over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.88,0:23:28.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.61,0:23:32.45,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Guess I really did die...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, he's still breathing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:37.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.02,0:23:38.86,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I'm alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.86,0:23:42.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ah! That poison must not work on humans!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.36,0:23:44.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay with me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:45.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you stand up, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.83,0:23:47.32,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Little boy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.63,0:24:08.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I shrunk?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.47,0:24:09.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.94,0:24:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,M-My name's Shinâ€”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.34,0:24:13.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Err...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.28,0:24:15.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um... Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.74,0:24:17.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.75,0:24:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are you going, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.68,0:24:21.84,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.49,0:24:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan: "The Kidnapping of the Company President's Daughter"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.30,0:24:36.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint: Skyscraper
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.33,0:24:39.14,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Challenge me next time!
